Teresa Greenway is an instructor of sourdough baking courses available on Udemy.com. Teresa has been successful with courses that are not usually thought to be highly successful, like for instance, the tech, business and entrepreneur courses. She has an online business called Northwest Sourdough, a four volume book called, "Discovering Sourdough" and a Youtube Channel. She also recently published her memoir, titled, "Reach for Joy" in which she chronicles her escape from an abusive marriage.
